               <p>handkerchief—I had had it two minutes before—I saw the prisoner walk<lb></lb>ing behind me, and called out, "I have lost my handkerchief—the prisoner asked for an explanation, and whether I suspected him—he walked on, and my friend made some observation—the prisoner was jpven in charge, and my handkerchief was found close to where he was.</p>
